92
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:33,920
Okay? They would maybe lie in the fields.

93
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:37,620
Because now and then, some
helots would break curfew.

94
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:40,820
They would, at midnight, try
to sneak out and have some fun.

95
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:43,700
And if you, as a Spartan young man,

96
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:48,040
