106
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:18,380
And this focused on maintaining
control in the Pelonese.

107
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:23,900
So the Spartans were not at all
interested in foreign policy.

108
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:28,240
Okay? They had absolutely no
interest in the world outside Sparta.

109
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:33,320
The Spartans, as a culture,
was very conservative.

110
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:36,100
Okay? They liked the way that...

111
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:38,100
They liked the way...

112
