They wanted things to stay the way...

113
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:48,160
They are. So it was a
very conformist culture.

114
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:54,500
Now and then you had
some kings or individuals

115
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:55,740
