116
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:58,240
The Spartans would kill those people.

117
00:06:58,340 --> 00:07:02,700
Okay? You were not allowed
to question authority.

118
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:05,800
You were not allowed to
promote change in Sparta.

119
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,760
The Spartans were also isolationists.

120
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:12,360
Okay? Their entire society was
a society of isolationists.

121
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:15,340
Their entire policy was, if you leave
us alone, we'll leave you alone.

122
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:18,040
Okay? And so that

123
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:21,780
was the society of Sparta.

124
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,120
When you think about it, in many ways,

125
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:28,180
