00:43:45,940 --> 00:43:48,440
lasts from about 431

775
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:52,040
BC to 404 BCE,

776
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:56,300
27 years, that Athens loses its empire.

777
00:43:56,520 --> 00:43:59,860
Okay? So, the culture, eudaimonia,

778
00:44:00,140 --> 00:44:05,400
that causes Athens to rise will
